data.description: Updated Beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath home in Huntington Forest on large lot with lots of upgrades! Outside features an open front porch with plenty of room for chairs, a bench or swing. Nice sized fenced backyard with newer storage shed and a back patio perfect for relaxing, barbecuing and or entertaining. Gutters recently replaced for proper draining.  Inside features beautiful vinyl plank flooring throughout main area of home and an updated kitchen with Quartz countertops and a breakfast bar. The kitchen opens up to the dining room which can also be used as the family room. Split Floorplan includes an inviting foyer with a formal living room, formal dining room or office and nice sized primary and spare bedrooms and closets. This house also features a new water heater and a ring doorbell. Convenient to I-295 and I-95, plenty of close by shopping and restaurants. This well maintained Mandarin home is a must see!
